graph TB
    Client[Client Request] --> Middleware{AuthGuardMiddleware}
    
    Middleware --> CheckHeader[Check Authorization Header]
    CheckHeader --> HasToken{Has Bearer Token?}
    
    HasToken -->|No| Return401[Return 401 Unauthorized]
    HasToken -->|Yes| ValidateJWT[Validate JWT Token]
    
    ValidateJWT --> JWTValid{JWT Valid?}
    JWTValid -->|No| Return401
    JWTValid -->|Yes| ExtractClaims[Extract user_id from Claims]
    
    ExtractClaims --> SetContext[Set request.state.user_id]
    SetContext --> CheckCSRF{POST/PUT/DELETE?}
    
    CheckCSRF -->|No| AllowRequest[Allow Request]
    CheckCSRF -->|Yes| ValidateOrigin[Validate Origin Header]
    
    ValidateOrigin --> OriginValid{Origin Valid?}
    OriginValid -->|No| Return403[Return 403 Forbidden - CSRF]
    OriginValid -->|Yes| AllowRequest
    
    AllowRequest --> Handler[Route Handler]
    Handler --> Database[(Database Query<br/>WHERE user_id = ?)]
    
    style Middleware fill:#e1f5fe
    style ValidateJWT fill:#fff3e0
    style CheckCSRF fill:#fce4ec
    style Database fill:#e8f5e8